Enum EventTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventTypes>
      • eu.ehri.project.definitions.EventTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EventTypes>

    public enum EventTypes
extends Enum<EventTypes>
    Event types are used to log actions performed in the system. These are the types of actions supported by the system.
